snippet: SINKMAN--Ellen. The Institute for Psychoanalytic Training and Research mourns the untimely death of Ellen Sinkman, esteemed member and colleague. Her warmth, intelligence and strong commitment to psychoanalysis will be deeply missed. 1/3
